{"tid":2206212,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄：香港民族後裔須接受黨安法的時代命運 正制訂教材及大綱再教育","createTime":"2020-09-17T10:49:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T11:02:34.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e2840a27d5c74e1bc39279deb59dec93fec25d25","tid":2206212,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T10:49:55.000Z","msg":"楊潤雄：正制訂港區國安法相關教材和課程大綱<br />\n<br />\n教育局長楊潤雄表示，香港對國家安全的概念相對陌生，當局正制訂港區國安法相關的教材和課程大綱，強調不論教師的立場，都有責任帶動學生了立法精神和影響。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄接受一個電視台專訪時表示，疫情仍會維持一段時間，學校要有心理準備，一旦有學生或教職員確診，學校要暫停開放，在家學習和面授課堂或會不斷交替。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2357686\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2357686&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNONOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=cfa1962b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2357686</a>"},{"pid":"2bee0c64da93804f81550ea7572127612eda0702","tid":2206212,"uid":286897,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T10:51:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df708a0eb0b7cf8c98b5609f55f02de877981e26","tid":2206212,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T10:52:41.000Z","msg":"香港變成一個大型再教育營"},{"pid":"0a14665e04b6daa33cb21a4663340880c4aae9de","tid":2206212,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T10:54:13.000Z","msg":"黨安法會否取代聖經地位?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ccdbd3e75b83b4e0331fa05fe745fe8fdcd7f31","tid":2206212,"uid":68669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T10:55:49.000Z","msg":"咁搞即係逼D有小朋友既家庭走，尤其是淺藍個班，佢地支持一國兩制但係完全將中國個套搬黎香港就一定唔制"},{"pid":"bd66e84be7508814d4d7c2f592b46a1149671437","tid":2206212,"uid":49609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T10:57:05.000Z","msg":"會唔會叫佢自己啲仔女讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec04aa5b0bd89215fa35f2eb3eed4e1af52f6f72","tid":2206212,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bee0c64da93804f81550ea7572127612eda0702","tid":2206212,"uid":286897,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T10:51:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T11:00:55.000Z","msg":"放學加堂講 搞到成埋學生憎到入心就啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc5d15c020a0c1c93337b4b0548ef00e891eaa4","tid":2206212,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd66e84be7508814d4d7c2f592b46a1149671437","tid":2206212,"uid":49609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T10:57:05.000Z","msg":"會唔會叫佢自己啲仔女讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T11:01:14.000Z","msg":"子女均讀國際學校 楊潤雄稱因港教育制度「複雜」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/128381/%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E5%9D%87%E8%AE%80%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1-%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84%E7%A8%B1%E5%9B%A0%E6%B8%AF%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6-%E8%A4%87%E9%9B%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F128381%2F%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%259D%2587%25E8%25AE%2580%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25A0%25A1-%25E6%25A5%258A%25E6%25BD%25A4%25E9%259B%2584%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25BA%25A6-%25E8%25A4%2587%25E9%259B%259C&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNONOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=218e9ae2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/128381/%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E5%9D%87%E8%AE%80%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1-%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84%E7%A8%B1%E5%9B%A0%E6%B8%AF%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6-%E8%A4%87%E9%9B%9C</a><br />\n楊潤雄自上任教育局局長後，已屢次被質疑，其子女過去並非就讀主流地區學校。據了解，楊育有兩名子女，他們過去均就讀國際學校，目前則在澳洲讀大學。他昨日接受Now新聞台訪問，坦承兩名子女過去均就讀國際學校，因為他派往外地工作回來後，覺得香港教育制度較「複雜」，而此舉亦「方便適應」。他表示希望將國際學校教學理念引入香港，但強調香港教育制度亦做出很多成績，在國際間備受推崇。他又認為自己其中一個子女，如果當年在傳統學校就讀，表現或會更好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家係澳洲讀大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14f37a98a8fa537478082cc47186a6bc0030c63","tid":2206212,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T11:02:34.000Z","msg":"標題黨 拉"}]}